the algorithm you used?\\\",\\n          \\\"Can you describe a situation where you had to choose between different data structures or algorithms?\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question\\\": \\\"Discuss your experience with cloud computing platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP. Have you worked with any specific services or tools?\\\",\\n        \\\"category\\\": \\\"Cloud Computing\\\",\\n        \\\"follow_up\\\": [\\n          \\\"What are the advantages and disadvantages of using cloud services?\\\",\\n          \\\"How do you ensure security in the cloud?\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n       {\\n        \\\"question\\\": \\\"How do you approach writing unit and integration tests? Can you provide an example of a time when testing helped you prevent a major bug?\\\",\\n        \\\"category\\\": \\\"Testing\\\",\\n        \\\"follow_up\\\": [\\n          \\\"What testing frameworks are you familiar with?\\\",\\n          \\\"How do you measure test coverage?\\\"\\n        ]\\n      }\\n    ],\\n    \\\"behavioral\\\": [\\n      {\\n        \\\"question\\\": \\\"Describe a time when you had to collaborate with a cross-functional team to achieve a goal. What were the challenges, and how did you overcome them?\\\",\\n        \\\"category\\\": \\\"Teamwork\\\",\\n        \\\"follow_up\\\": [\\n          \\\"What was your role in the team?\\\",\\n          \\\"How did you handle conflicting priorities?\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question\\\": \\\"Tell me about a time when you faced a significant technical challenge. What steps did you take to resolve it?\\\",\\n        \\\"category\\\": \\\"Problem Solving\\\",\\n        \\\"follow_up\\\": [\\n          \\\"What resources did you use to find a solution?\\\",\\n          \\\"What did you learn from this experience?\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question\\\": \\\"Describe a situation where you had to learn a new technology or skill quickly. How did you approach 