er(s):  \\n  • Jane Smith, Engineering Manager  \\n  • Bob Lee, Senior Software Engineer  \\n\\nPlease reply to confirm your availability. If this slot does not work for you, let me know two alternative times this week and we will accommodate your schedule.\\n\\nWe look forward to learning more about your experience and answering any questions you may have.\\n\\nBest regards,\\n\\nMary Johnson  \\nTalent Acquisition Partner  \\nExample Corp  \\nmary.johnson@examplecorp.com  \\n(555) 123-4567\\n\\n---\\n\\nSubject: Follow-Up on Your Interview – Software Engineer Position\\n\\nDear John Doe,\\n\\nI hope you are doing well.\\n\\nThank you again for interviewing with us on Tuesday, July 16th for the Software Engineer role. We enjoyed discussing your contributions to microservices architecture and your approach to system design.\\n\\nWe are currently reviewing all candidate feedback and expect to share our decision by Friday, July 26, 2024. In the meantime, please let me know if you have any additional questions or would like further information about the team or role.\\n\\nThank you for your time and interest in Example Corp. We appreciate your patience and look forward to being in touch soon.\\n\\nSincerely,\\n\\nMary Johnson  \\nTalent Acquisition Partner  \\nExample Corp  \\nmary.johnson@examplecorp.com  \\n(555) 123-4567\"}"}
{"timestamp": "2026-05-26 16:17:25,014", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.validation", "module": "logging_config", "function": "log_gpt_conversation", "line": 403, "message": "{\n  \"event_type\": \"gpt_conversation\",\n  \"task_id\": \"task_7\",\n  \"conversation_type\": \"task_execution\",\n  \"iteration\": 1,\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"system\",\n      \"content\": \"\\n# Role:\\nHelp me produce a precise and detailed solution for the given task. Follow these instructions exactly:\\n\\n# Objective & Steps:\\n1. Ensure Completeness:\\n   - Avoid placeholders or incomplete text.\\n   - Your output must meet all requirements of the task.\\n   - Include all necessary details so that the output is self-contained and can be directly used as input for downstream tasks.\\n\\n2. Maintain Precision and Clarity:\\n   - Your output will be used as input for subsequent tasks; therefore, it must be comprehensive and precise.\\n   - **Output the answer only without any jusifications**\\n\\n3. Avoid Repetition:\\n   - Do not repeat verbatim any content from previous tasks.\\n   - Ensure your output is original and adds value to the workflow.\\n\\n\\n\\n# Audience:\\nYour output will be used as a solution for the given task, it will be used in the later validation and intergration process.\\n\\n\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"# **The Overall Goal**\\nPerform interview and candidate evaluation for a candidate.\\n- Analyze job descriptions and candidate resumes\\n- Conduct  interviews with technical and behavioral questions\\n- Ask follow-up questions based on candidate responses\\n- Evaluate candidate answers for relevance, depth, confidence, and technical accuracy\\n- Score candidates across multiple evaluation categories\\n- Generate recruiter communication emails such as interview invitations and follow-ups\\n- Produce a final candidate evaluation report containing:\\n    - Resume-job match analysis\\n    - Interview summary\