"What are some common API design patterns you've used?\\\",\\n          \\\"How do you ensure your APIs are secure and performant?\\\"\\n        ],\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\\"REST APIs\\\", \\\"System Design\\\", \\\"Security\\\"]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question\\\": \\\"Explain your experience with SQL. Can you describe a time when you had to optimize a slow-running query?\\\",\\n        \\\"follow_up\\\": [\\n          \\\"What tools did you use to identify the bottleneck?\\\",\\n          \\\"What specific techniques did you use to optimize the query?\\\",\\n          \\\"How did you measure the performance improvement?\\\"\\n        ],\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\\"SQL\\\", \\\"Database\\\", \\\"Performance Tuning\\\"]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question\\\": \\\"Describe your experience with cloud computing platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP. What services have you used, and for what purposes?\\\",\\n        \\\"follow_up\\\": [\\n          \\\"How have you used cloud services to improve scalability and reliability?\\\",\\n          \\\"What are some of the cost optimization strategies you've employed in the cloud?\\\",\\n          \\\"How do you approach security in the cloud environment?\\\"\\n        ],\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\\"Cloud Computing\\\", \\\"AWS/Azure/GCP\\\", \\\"System Design\\\"]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question\\\": \\\"Explain the concept of Agile development methodologies. What is your experience working in Agile teams?\\\",\\n        \\\"follow_up\\\": [\\n          \\\"Describe your role in the Agile team and your responsibilities.\\\",\\n          \\\"How do you handle conflicts or disagreements within an Agile team?\\\",\\n          \\\"What are some of the challenges you've faced working in an Agile environment and how did you overcome them?\\\"\\n        ],\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\\"Agile development methodologies\\\", \\\"Teamwork\\\", \\\"Communication\